&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Bidease&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bidease is a fast-growing mobile ad tech company specializing in &lt;strong&gt;in-app programmatic advertising&lt;/strong&gt;. Our DSP empowers advertisers to efficiently reach their target audiences across mobile devices. We work with top brands, agencies, and app developers to drive measurable growth through data-driven performance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an Ad Operations professional with strong analytical skills and a deep understanding of performance marketing. The ideal candidate will excel at executing, optimizing, and scaling performance-based advertising campaigns while tailoring strategies to best fit each client’s goals. This role requires a blend of ad tech expertise, data analytics, and operational efficiency to drive measurable outcomes. You will be hands-on in campaign execution, leveraging machine learning and predictive analytics to improve decision-making, maximize efficiency, and boost ROI.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Grow and scale client accounts&lt;/strong&gt; through strategic planning, continuous optimization, and efficient resource allocation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Act as a strategic partner&lt;/strong&gt; to Sales and Customer Success teams, providing actionable insights that drive performance and retention.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own end-to-end campaign management&lt;/strong&gt;, from client onboarding to full campaign lifecycle execution, with a focus on maximizing results and customer value.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Leverage data-driven insights, machine learning models, and automation&lt;/strong&gt; to enhance campaign performance and operational efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Conduct A/B testing and performance analysis&lt;/strong&gt; to uncover growth opportunities and refine optimization strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Monitor and mitigate risks&lt;/strong&gt; related to ad fraud, invalid traffic, and other performance-impacting factors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaborate with Product and Engineering teams&lt;/strong&gt;, providing structured feedback and strategic input on new features, product improvements, and workflow enhancements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years of experience in performance mobile advertising, programmatic, or ad tech&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep knowledge of ad platforms, RTB, MMPs and programmatic trading.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience managing high-budget ad campaigns with a strong focus on ROAS and revenue growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong problem-solving, analytical, and strategic thinking abilities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Join Bidease?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Bidease, we believe in empowering our people and fostering a dynamic work environment. Our benefits include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
